title: Hour 1 -Tua, Tua, Tua!
itunes:title: Hour 1 -Tua, Tua, Tua!
description:
There is only one story dominating the sports landscape this morning and Dan dives deep into Miami Dolphins QB Tua Tagovailoa's injuries over his past two games and asks all the questions that probably should have been answered before Tua stepped on the field last night.
